title: [Musette's Outfitting]
[Musette's General Store]
description: White silk-paneled walls rise from a woven seagrass floor.  Just above a potted palm tree hangs a wall-mounted blowfish, and a sturdy bamboo-rafter ceiling completes the picture.  An oversized sea chest and a salt-crusted sandstone case stand side by side in the middle of the room.
